textBeforeTable: Older editions of DB2 and IMS Tools publications are available at the IBM Publications Center. To submit general feedback about the IBM Knowledge Center experience, send email to ibmkc@us.ibm.com. IBM Knowledge Center is now the official home for DB2 Tools technical product documentation.
